{
    "esm": "0.4.0",
    "metadata": {
        "name": "SoilWaterEquilibrium",
        "description": "Layer-averaged equilibrium volumetric water content (θ_E, Eq. 5.101) and equilibrium matric potential at the layer node (ψ_E, Eq. 5.106) for a single soil layer, following Oleson et al. (2010, CLM4 Tech Note Ch. 5, §5.3.2.1, Eqs. 5.98–5.106). θ_E is fully saturated (θ_sat) when the water table is above the layer (z_v < z_h_upper), otherwise is computed by integrating the hydrostatic-equilibrium Clapp-Hornberger profile across the layer, clamped to [0, θ_sat]. ψ_E is derived from the Brooks-Corey inverse relation with a 1% saturation floor and a hard lower bound at ψ_min = −10⁵ m to prevent numerical underflow. Migrated from UrbanCanopy.jl@9200edd4 src/hydrology.jl:509 (`SoilWaterEquilibrium` @component). Note: the migration-tracker row for this component carried the blocking_gap `other:discretization-plan` because the row description mentioned an in-file Richards-equation PDE at src/hydrology.jl:674. Inspection shows that PDESystem lives in a separate non-`@component` helper function (`RichardsEquation`) and is not part of `SoilWaterEquilibrium`, which is a plain two-equation algebraic `@component`. No discretization plan is needed.",
        "tags": [
            "urban_canopy",
            "hydrology",
            "soil",
            "clapp-hornberger",
            "equilibrium",
            "observed-only",
            "clmu"
        ],
        "created": "2026-05-21T00:00:00Z",
        "authors": [
            "UrbanCanopy.jl contributors",
            "EarthSciModels migration (esm-4kir)"
        ],
        "references": [
            {
                "citation": "Oleson, K. W., et al. (2010). Technical Description of version 4.0 of the Community Land Model (CLM). NCAR Technical Note NCAR/TN-478+STR. Chapter 5 (Soil and Snow Hydrology), Section 5.3.2.1 (Equilibrium Soil Water Content), Eqs. 5.98–5.106, pp. 136–138."
            }
        ]
    },
    "models": {
        "SoilWaterEquilibrium": {
            "reference": {
                "notes": "source_ref: UrbanCanopy.jl@9200edd4f15609f20339d3a7d104de8064544310:src/hydrology.jl:509\nUpstream `SoilWaterEquilibrium` is an MTK `@component` with six `@parameters` (θ_sat, ψ_sat, B, z_h_upper, z_h_lower, z_v) and two time-indexed `@variables` (θ_E, ψ_E) given by two algebraic equations with no derivatives. Identical structure preserved here.\n\nThe upstream component declares one `@constants` block: `ψ_min = -1.0e5 m` (minimum matric potential, converted from the CLM4 value −10⁸ mm). Per the convention of sibling files in this directory (groundwater_drainage.esm, surface_runoff_infiltration.esm), `@constants` are promoted to parameters with fixed defaults so MTK's unit checker is satisfied and the equation AST references them by name.\n\nTracker blocking_gap clarification: the migration-tracker row for this bead read `blocking_gap: other:discretization-plan` because the row description mentioned `internally builds Richards-eq PDE (:674) via MOLFiniteDifference`. Inspecting the source shows that `RichardsEquation` (the PDESystem builder, lines 597–683) is a separate non-`@component` helper function that is never called by `SoilWaterEquilibrium`. `SoilWaterEquilibrium` itself (lines 509–558) is a plain algebraic `@component` — two equations, no PDESystem, no MOLFiniteDifference. No discretization plan is needed.\n\nEquation 1 (θ_E, Eqs. 5.101–5.102 simplified): The upstream docstring notes that the code uses `z_v < z_h_upper` as the only branch point (fully-saturated guard), then applies Eq. 5.101 with Eq. 5.105 clamping for all other cases including the water-table-within-layer zone (z_h_upper ≤ z_v ≤ z_h_lower). The Clapp-Hornberger integral term uses the ratio `(ψ_sat − z_v + z_h_x)/ψ_sat` raised to the exponent `(1 − 1/B)`. When z_v is in the transition zone near z_h_upper, this ratio can become negative (since ψ_sat is small and negative), making the power non-real; the outer `max(0·θ_sat, …)` clamp absorbs any NaN result that symbolic evaluators may produce in that region. All inline tests deliberately target the two well-defined branches: z_v < z_h_upper (saturated) and z_v > z_h_lower + |ψ_sat| (fully below the layer, valid real domain).\n\nEquation 2 (ψ_E, Eq. 5.106): `ψ_E = max(ψ_sat · (max(θ_E, 0.01·θ_sat)/θ_sat)^(−B), ψ_min)`. The `max(θ_E, 0.01·θ_sat)` inner floor prevents division-by-zero or extreme negative potentials when θ_E → 0. The outer `max(·, ψ_min)` with ψ_min = −10⁵ m clamps ψ_E at the physically plausible floor (the clamping activates when the Brooks-Corey formula would give ψ_raw < −10⁵ m, which occurs when the effective saturation ratio (θ_E/θ_sat) < approximately (|ψ_sat|/|ψ_min|)^(1/B); for typical CLM4 sandy-loam params that threshold is ~0.011).\n\nUnicode parameter and variable names (θ_sat, ψ_sat, ψ_min, θ_E, ψ_E) are preserved verbatim from upstream — sibling files in this directory and the temps/ subdirectory already established unicode identifiers as the rig convention (soil_water_flux.esm, freezing_point_depression.esm, interface_hydraulic_conductivity.esm, water_table_depth.esm).\n\nDefault parameter values: θ_sat = 0.434, ψ_sat = −0.036 m, B = 4.05 are CLM4 Table 5.1 sandy-loam soil-texture values. z_h_upper = 0.05 m, z_h_lower = 0.25 m are typical top-of-column layer interfaces; z_v = 1.0 m is a mid-range water-table depth that places the layer in the well-defined unsaturated domain and yields a non-trivial θ_E. The `ψ_min` constant default matches the upstream `@constants` value exactly.\n\nObservability classification: this component is functionally observed-only — both outputs are given by algebraic equations in terms of the parameters (the `(t)` time index has no role since there are no derivatives). Test scenarios use `time_span: [0, 1]` and sample at t=0 following the convention of sibling observed-only ESM files in this directory.\n\nTolerance rationale (model-level rel=1e-9): observed-only algebraic system (no ODE integration). The longest evaluation chain involves one power (`^`) call per bracketed term (≈1–2 ULP relative error), one subtraction, one multiplication, and one max/min clamp — worst-case roundoff ~10×ULP ≈ 1e-15. 1e-9 leaves six orders of headroom. Saturated-branch assertions (θ_E = θ_sat, ψ_E = ψ_sat by exact arithmetic) use `abs: 1e-15` to gate stuck-at-zero/stuck-at-constant regressions."
            },
            "tolerance": {
                "rel": 1.0e-9
            },
            "variables": {
                "θ_sat": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m^3/m^3",
                    "default": 0.434,
                    "description": "Porosity (volumetric saturation, Clapp-Hornberger Eq. 5.71)"
                },
                "ψ_sat": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": -0.036,
                    "description": "Saturated matric potential (negative by convention, CLM4 Table 5.1 sandy loam, Eq. 5.74)"
                },
                "B": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 4.05,
                    "description": "Clapp-Hornberger exponent (dimensionless, CLM4 Table 5.1 sandy loam, Eq. 5.72)"
                },
                "z_h_upper": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 0.05,
                    "description": "Depth of the upper interface of the soil layer (positive downward from surface)"
                },
                "z_h_lower": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 0.25,
                    "description": "Depth of the lower interface of the soil layer (positive downward from surface)"
                },
                "z_v": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 1.0,
                    "description": "Water table depth (positive downward from surface, Eq. 5.101 input)"
                },
                "ψ_min": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": -100000.0,
                    "description": "Minimum matric potential floor (converted from −10⁸ mm; upstream @constants, Eq. 5.106 hard lower bound)"
                },
                "θ_E": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "m^3/m^3",
                    "description": "Layer-averaged equilibrium volumetric water content (Oleson Eq. 5.101)"
                },
                "ψ_E": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "m",
                    "description": "Equilibrium matric potential at the layer node (Oleson Eq. 5.106)"
                }
            },
            "equations": [
                {
                    "lhs": "θ_E",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "ifelse",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "<",
                                "args": ["z_v", "z_h_upper"]
                            },
                            "θ_sat",
                            {
                                "op": "max",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": [0.0, "θ_sat"]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "op": "min",
                                        "args": [
                                            "θ_sat",
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "/",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "*",
                                                                "args": ["θ_sat", "ψ_sat"]
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "*",
                                                                "args": [
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "-",
                                                                        "args": ["z_h_lower", "z_h_upper"]
                                                                    },
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "-",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            1.0,
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "/",
                                                                                "args": [1.0, "B"]
                                                                            }
                                                                        ]
                                                                    }
                                                                ]
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "-",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "^",
                                                                "args": [
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "/",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "+",
                                                                                "args": [
                                                                                    {
                                                                                        "op": "-",
                                                                                        "args": ["ψ_sat", "z_v"]
                                                                                    },
                                                                                    "z_h_lower"
                                                                                ]
                                                                            },
                                                                            "ψ_sat"
                                                                        ]
                                                                    },
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "-",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            1.0,
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "/",
                                                                                "args": [1.0, "B"]
                                                                            }
                                                                        ]
                                                                    }
                                                                ]
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "^",
                                                                "args": [
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "/",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "+",
                                                                                "args": [
                                                                                    {
                                                                                        "op": "-",
                                                                                        "args": ["ψ_sat", "z_v"]
                                                                                    },
                                                                                    "z_h_upper"
                                                                                ]
                                                                            },
                                                                            "ψ_sat"
                                                                        ]
                                                                    },
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "-",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            1.0,
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "/",
                                                                                "args": [1.0, "B"]
                                                                            }
                                                                        ]
                                                                    }
                                                                ]
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "ψ_E",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "max",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    "ψ_sat",
                                    {
                                        "op": "^",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "/",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "max",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            "θ_E",
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "*",
                                                                "args": [0.01, "θ_sat"]
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "θ_sat"
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "op": "-",
                                                "args": [0.0, "B"]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            "ψ_min"
                        ]
                    }
                }
            ],
            "tests": [
                {
                    "id": "saturated_above_water_table",
                    "description": "Water table well above the layer (z_v = 0.0 m < z_h_upper = 0.05 m): ifelse condition is true so θ_E = θ_sat = 0.434 m³/m³ exactly (Eq. 5.101 saturated branch). ψ_E = max(ψ_sat · 1^(−B), ψ_min) = ψ_sat = −0.036 m (fully saturated, Brooks-Corey at θ/θ_sat = 1). Verifies the saturated branch of both equations.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
                        "θ_sat": 0.434,
                        "ψ_sat": -0.036,
                        "B": 4.05,
                        "z_h_upper": 0.05,
                        "z_h_lower": 0.25,
                        "z_v": 0.0,
                        "ψ_min": -100000.0
                    },
                    "time_span": { "start": 0.0, "end": 1.0 },
                    "assertions": [
                        { "variable": "θ_E", "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.434, "tolerance": { "abs": 1.0e-15 } },
                        { "variable": "ψ_E", "time": 0.0, "expected": -0.036, "tolerance": { "abs": 1.0e-15 } }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "saturated_just_below_upper_interface",
                    "description": "Water table just inside the saturated branch (z_v = 0.03 m < z_h_upper = 0.05 m): ifelse condition still true, θ_E = θ_sat = 0.434, ψ_E = −0.036 m. Exercises the saturated branch at a non-zero z_v close to the branch boundary.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
                        "θ_sat": 0.434,
                        "ψ_sat": -0.036,
                        "B": 4.05,
                        "z_h_upper": 0.05,
                        "z_h_lower": 0.25,
                        "z_v": 0.03,
                        "ψ_min": -100000.0
                    },
                    "time_span": { "start": 0.0, "end": 1.0 },
                    "assertions": [
